name: Baby Solana
description:
bsol is expected as a game universe backed by a strong and talented Vietnamese team with the hope of turning P2E games into the future of digital assets. Bsol is currently developing its very first project called bsol World, a tactics-based game allowing people to interact with one another in the virtual world we create.
 sol World is expected to compete with all existing NFTs games on the world right now and bsol tokens will play the same role of “AXS” in “Axie Infinity”.
